Good Morning, confronting your fear fear is easier when you move towards it. You will figure it out as you go. Not moving causes fear to paralyze you. If you allow yourself the chance to face your fears, you find out it is not as big as you think.

 On my bucket list I had skydiving, I figured I would wait till I was ancient to do it. Well, I got the opportunity to do it a couple of years ago, and no I'm not Ancient. I'm 36 today lol.i have a huge fear of heights, but when I did it I was physically way too high for my mind to register the height. No I wasn't on drugs lol At that height it  reminded me of riding in an airplane.  As we began to free fall there were no rush of blood falling similar to the feeling of riding a roller coaster. It wasn't like that. It was calm, but I was in so much pain from my weight on the harness that I wanted to be on the ground quickly lol

After I had the experience, it was not at all scary as what I thought it would be. I find alot of things in life are the same.
What are some things you are afraid of? Place it in the comment below.

"👁️‍🗨 10 Things to Look Out for to Avoid Modeling Agency Scams:

1. **Payment to Join:** Never pay to join a legitimate agency; they earn from your work, not upfront fees.

2. **Birthday Suit Pics:** Be cautious if asked for revealing photos; this isn't standard for commercial modeling.

3. **In-House Photographer Fees:** If they profit from in-house photographers, it might be a scam. 

4. **Mall Search Competitions:** Legit agencies don't guarantee contracts through paid competitions.

5. **Unprofessional Behavior:** If they get rude for asking questions about the contract, it's a red flag.

6. **Inappropriate Grooming:** Stay safe from agencies that want something more from you than your success as a model. Read between the lines

7. **Research & Reviews:** Check for reviews; reputable agencies have an online presence.

8. **Professional Images:** Legitimate agencies showcase professional work on their website.

9. **Overpromising:** Be wary of agencies promising instant stardom; success takes time and effort.

10. **Talk to Models:** Connect with models who've been with the agency for 6+ months for insights.

Stay smart and protect your modeling dreams! 💼✨ #ModelingScamAwareness #fitness #fit #modeling #bodybuilder
